data.description: WELCOME HOME TO YOUR BEAUTIFUL SINGLE LEVEL CORNER LOT HOME!!!  THIS STUNNING HOME HAS GREAT CURB APPEAL WITH LUSH WELCOMING LANDSCAPING.  ENTER INTO THE SPACIOUS FORMAL LIVING & DINING WITH NEWER LAMINATE FLOORING, WOOD SHUTTERS AND AN ABUNDANCE OF NATURAL SUNLIGHT.  THE SPACIOUS KITCHEN BOASTS NEWER STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, DOUBLE CONVECTION OVEN, 5 BURNER COOKTOP, MICROWAVE, STAINLESS STEEL APRON- FRONT SINK, PULL OUT SHELVING IN THE CABINETS, GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, LARGE EAT AT ISLAND ALL OPEN TO THE SPACIOUS FAMILY ROOM WHICH IS FANTASTIC FOR ENTERAINING.  THE LARGE MASTER BEDROOM BOASTS 3 LARGE WINDOWS LOOKING INTO THE MANICURED BACKYARD AND HAS A SPACIOUS EN-SUITE WITH WALK-IN SHOWER AND SOAKING TUB.  DOWN THE HALL YOU WILL FIND GREAT STORAGE & LINEN CABINETS, TWO SPACIOUS SECONDARY BEDROOMS, SECONDARY BATHROOM WITH DOUBLE SINKS AND A LAUNDRY ROOM WITH UTILITY SINK.  THE GARAGE HAS AN INSULATED GARAGE DOOR WITH NEW SPRINGS, OVERHEAD STORAGE, AND NEW WATER HEATER.  THE RELAXING PRIVATE BACKYARD HAS DROUGHT TOLERANT TURF AND LUSH PLANTS ALL AROUND WITH IMPROVED DRAINAGE AND RAIN GUTTERS.
